Summary: Defines the properties of the VoxelGI node, including camera attributes, data, size, and subdivision level.

Properties:
- camera_attributes (CameraAttributes): The camera attributes used for VoxelGI.
- data (VoxelGIData): The VoxelGI data.
- size (Vector3): The size of the VoxelGI grid. Default: Vector3(20, 20, 20).
- subdiv (Subdiv): The subdivision level of the VoxelGI grid. Default: 1.
