Path: godot/classes/class_voxelgi.rst
Summary: This section describes the methods and enumerations available for the VoxelGI class in Godot Engine.

Methods
Method: bake(from_node: Node = null, create_visual_debug: bool = false) → void
Method: debug_bake() → void

Enumerations
enum Subdiv:
  SUBDIV_64 = 0
  Use 64 subdivisions. This is the lowest quality setting, but the fastest. Use it if you can, but especially use it on lower-end hardware.
  SUBDIV_128 = 1
  Use 128 subdivisions. This is the default quality setting.
  SUBDIV_256 = 2
  Use 256 subdivisions.
  SUBDIV_512 = 3
  Use 512 subdivisions. This is the highest quality setting, but the slowest. On lower-end hardware, this could cause the GPU to stall.
  SUBDIV_MAX = 4
  Represents the size of the Subdiv enum.
